            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#哪些因素可能诱发抑郁#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】上海的张女士因为工作压力大，精神极度紧张，觉得没人能理解她，经常睡到半夜突然就醒来，甚至有了轻生的念头，于是到医院检查，诊断出得了抑郁症。⚠️医生提醒，工作、生活中有重大变故和长期慢性的压力、饮食睡眠不规律等因素都容易诱发抑郁。如果流露出消极的想法和迹象，比如脑海里反复出现关于死亡的念头等，应当尽快就医，必要时住院治疗。 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F4%E4%B8%AA%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F4%E4%B8%AA%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#抑郁症早期4个危险信号#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6WhZh8C" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
